summary: AN ORDINANCE approving a further modification of the urban renewal plan for the Yesler-Atlantic Neighborhood Project (No. Wash. R-5) approved by Ordinance 96123 as amended by Ordinance 101665, to redesignate the area bounded generally by 23rd Avenue South, South Jackson Street, 25th Avenue South and South King Street from High Density Multiple to Community Shopping, adding certain exhibits and superseding certain exhibits.
